m shameless!"],[3666,3832,"I'm am, I'm shallow!"],[3832,3928,"Just please, just hit me!"],[3928,4049,"Hit me as much as you want!"],[4049,4108,"Hit me!"],[4129,4175,"No."],[4350,4491,"If you had accepted"],[4525,4654,"the Bloodveil Moonstone"],[4654,4763,"from me as a gift,"],[4763,4888,"then it would have been yours."],[4892,5017,"But now it's still mine."],[5075,5159,"So you owe me"],[5159,5338,"three billion dollars in damages."],[5447,5488,"What?"]],"38":[[0,25,"What?"],[25,83,"I don't have..."],[154,312,"I don't have three billion dollars."],[312,375,"I..."],[392,500,"If I don't mate with Caspian,"],[500,638,"I'll never have that kind of money."],[663,855,"What you can and can't afford"],[855,971,"is not my problem."],[1021,1134,"All I know is that you have to"],[1134,1276,"pay for this today."],[1376,1438,"Caspian,"],[1509,1622,"tell your sister to forgive me."],[1622,1747,"We can still be family, right?"],[1747,1910,"I mean, what's mine is yours,"],[1910,2002,"what's yours is mine,"],[2002,2118,"your sister's money is ours."],[2118,2227,"Why keep score?"],[2264,2323,"Family?"],[2373,2502,"You think that I would defend you"],[2502,2640,"after what you did to her?"],[2690,2857,"No, it wasn't my fault."],[2857,2961,"It wasn't my fault!"],[2961,3032,"It was Rowen!"],[3078,3136,"He did it."],[3140,3349,"He beat her until she lost her pup."],[3349,3424,"It was him."],[3428,3524,"He did it!"],[3557,3732,"You think that's what actually matters?"],[3732,3845,"You brought my sister here"],[3845,3983,"to humiliate her."],[3995,4091,"What about her pup?"],[4112,4195,"Her pup wouldn't be dead"],[4195,4300,"if it wasn't for you."],[4329,4567,"Caspian, please, don't you..."],[4713,4792,"Can't you forgive me?"],[4792,5096,"I, I mean, don't you care about me?"],[5096,5330,"Or, or am I just some, some, some toy"],[5330,5426,"you can toss aside"],[5426,5505,"when you're done with me?"],[5505,5563,"Toy?"],[5655,5739,"Don't flatter yourself."],[5739,5839,"You have less respect from me"],[5839,5980,"right now than a fucking flea."],[6006,6172,"I know you're still mad at me"],[6243,6523,"and I, I don't blame you."],[6564,6660,"To make it up to you."],[6660,6865,"I, I promise you can have as"],[6865,6990,"many she-wolf mistresses"],[6990,7082,"as you want."],[7144,7253,"And I, I'll treat them"],[7253,7399,"like best friends, like sisters"],[7399,7557,"and, I won't complain."],[7557,7603,"I won't,"],[7603,7753,"I won't ever make a fuss about it."],[7753,7932,"Just please, just please,"],[7932,8058,"please don't leave me."],[8174,8308,"Man, you don't give up, do you?"]],"39":[[58,196,"Man, you don't give up, do you?"],[254,483,"Caspian, I know you still love me."],[567,767,"I know what we have is real."],[838,1042,"I, I never should've doubted you."],[1076,1142,"I shouldn't have."],[1142,1326,"I should've listened to you but,"],[1326,1388,"I will."],[1388,1484,"I will from now on."],[1484,1651,"I'll, I'll listen to everything you say."],[1651,1735,"I promise."],[1768,1981,"Luna Marina, please."],[2118,2239,"See how earnestly"],[2239,2389,"my daughter is apologizing,"],[2423,2594,"can you please forgive her?"],[2752,2861,"It's, it's my fault."],[2865,2986,"I, I raised her."],[2986,3107,"I'm the one that spoiled her."],[3153,3299,"I promise I will keep her in line"],[3299,3349,"from now on."],[3349,3428,"I promise."],[3474,3624,"She's waited all of her life"],[3624,3787,"for her Luna coronation."],[3841,4095,"Please, don't let this terrible incident"],[4095,4295,"ruin hers and Caspian's happiness."],[4366,4683,"I would never ruin Caspian's happiness."],[4725,4771,"Oh."],[4859,4925,"Thank you."],[5080,5330,"But Caspian isn't desperate"],[5330,5388,"for a mate."],[5422,5593,"There are plenty of she-wolves"],[5601,5797,"that would kill for the opportunity"],[5797,5980,"to be mated with the Alpha"],[5980,6135,"of the Bloodveil pack."],[6272,6335,"I won't oppose."],[6477,6573,"With one exception."],[6619,6719,"Willow Hale,"],[6785,7027,"you will never be welcomed"],[7027,7169,"into the Bloodveil pack."]],"40":[[0,229,"You will never be welcomed"],[229,367,"into the Bloodveil pack."],[608,658,"No!"],[742,821,"I'm the only one"],[821,959,"who will mate with the Alpha!"],[1084,1155,"Caspian!"],[1205,1326,"Caspian, think of all the years"],[1326,1418,"we've spent together."],[1472,1655,"I mean, even if I can't be your Luna,"],[1655,1885,"I can, I can still be your mistress."],[1901,2010,"I, just please,"],[2010,2139,"please don't throw me away."],[2139,2168,"I..."],[2198,2314,"Willow, you're such a shame."],[2464,2581,"I don't know what I ever even saw in you."],[2606,2681,"It's you."],[2698,2777,"It's you."],[2777,2936,"It's always been you."],[2936,3199,"I, I'll never mate again!"],[3282,3470,"Luna Marina, please."],[3490,3707,"Please, tell Caspian to take me back."],[3762,3845,"Once we're family,"],[3845,3978,"I'll do anything you say."],[3978,4179,"I'll, I'll be your dog!"],[4179,4362,"I'll, I'll be at your beck and call,"],[4362,4421,"night and day!"],[4425,4525,"I'll, I'll, I'll..."],[4571,4746,"I'll, I'll do anything you ask!"],[4754,4909,"Please, just please."],[5005,5055,"How?"],[5125,5234,"My pup is dead."],[5301,5405,"Nothing you do"],[5405,5530,"can bring him back to me."]],"41":[[0,179,"Sis, what are you looking at me for?"],[200,325,"There's nothing I can do."],[333,442,"I mean it's not like she would take me"],[442,529,"to be her son."],[558,642,"It's not like mom would ever"],[642,738,"allow that to happen."],[771,842,"I agree."],[867,967,"Of course I agree."],[988,1063,"We all agree!"],[1226,1263,"Take him."],[1292,1380,"He won't be a part of"],[1380,1505,"our family anymore!"],[1526,1634,"He can be your son!"],[1689,1901,"You all think so highly of yourselves."],[1985,2085,"Why would I,"],[2143,2264,"Luna Marina Brooks,"],[2293,2464,"want him as my son?"],[2594,2640,"Willow,"],[2740,2873,"I believe you're a smart wolf."],[2944,3040,"If you can think of a way"],[3040,3132,"to make it up to me,"],[3178,3253,"I'll forgive you."],[3299,3461,"The Luna coronation can continue."],[3499,3611,"No, wait, Mari."],[3645,3716,"What?"],[4371,4416,"Rowen,"],[4487,4592,"don't you want your big sister"],[4592,4713,"to marry into the Bloodveil pack?"],[4775,4938,"I mean, yes."],[4988,5213,"But it's too late for that now."],[5213,5330,"You've gone too far."],[5330,5426,"There's nothing I can do."],[5430,5555,"I can think of one thing."],[5634,5705,"What?"],[5793,5897,"A life for a life?"]],"42":[[8,104,"Whoever killed Marina's pup"],[104,208,"can pay with his life."],[237,479,"Are you so desperate"],[500,738,"to marry into the royal wolf pack"],[738,829,"that you would actually"],[829,984,"just sacrifice your own brother?"],[1009,1126,"Caspian was very clear."],[1142,1247,"Whoever killed Marina's pup"],[1247,1317,"needs to die."],[1359,1476,"So if you're gonna die anyway,"],[1476,1593,"then when I marry into the"],[1593,1647,"Bloodveil pack,"],[1647,1760,"I'll buy you a very nice headstone,"],[1760,1830,"I'll come visit you-"],[1835,1914,"Willow!"],[2052,2256,"Rowen, beat that she-wolf"],[2256,2419,"until she miscarried."],[2448,2644,"How can you be so ruthless?"],[2681,2811,"Mom, think about it."],[2852,2982,"Once I marry into their pack,"],[3040,3136,"we're gonna have money, success,"],[3136,3253,"everything you ever wanted!"],[3303,3424,"She's heartless,"],[3461,3657,"throwing her brother away like that."],[3703,3903,"Marina Brooks is the scary one here."],[3945,4054,"A few words from her"],[4087,4216,"and Willow is losing it."],[4262,4312,"Wait!"],[4358,4408,"Sis."],[4446,4508,"Look at me."],[4546,4692,"Aren't you pregnant?"],[5121,5188,"How?"]],"43":[[8,271,"Sis, aren't you pregnant?"],[725,930,"This pup is the heir"],[955,1146,"to the legacy of the Bloodveil pack."],[1192,1288,"You wouldn't"],[1309,1455,"throw away the pup too,"],[1593,1634,"would you?"],[1689,1822,"Yes, Caspian, that's right."],[1822,2014,"I, I never told you, but, uh,"],[2085,2143,"I'm pregnant."],[2181,2381,"Oh my sweet baby."],[2460,2577,"That's wonderful news."],[2577,2702,"Why didn't you say so?"],[2702,2857,"Why didn't you tell us sooner?"],[2890,3069,"You see, Luna Marina,"],[3119,3303,"she's pregnant with Caspian's pup."],[3315,3520,"He has to claim her as his Luna now."],[3591,3757,"Oh, Caspian, is this really true?"],[3757,3858,"Is she really pregnant?"],[3858,3903,"No."],[4041,4183,"Willow, you think I'm fucking stupid?"],[4241,4308,"You wanted to wait"],[4308,4475,"until the Luna coronation today,"],[4517,4650,"so I decided to respect that."],[4658,4742,"I haven't touched you"],[4742,4888,"in the entirety of the three years"],[4888,5013,"that we've been together."],[5092,5134,"How could you"],[5134,5238,"possibly be pregnant?"]],"44":[[0,79,"I haven't touched you"],[79,229,"in the entirety of the three years"],[229,342,"that we've been together."],[383,513,"Never touched her?"],[558,696,"Then she can't be pregnant."],[709,917,"Yeah, he must be making shit up"],[917,1009,"just to stay alive."],[1009,1055,"No!"],[1134,1242,"It's all true."],[1288,1468,"I snuck into my sister's room"],[1488,1614,"and I found an ultrasound"],[1614,1705,"from our healer."],[1876,1931,"Look."],[2560,2623,"Very well."],[2861,2990,"I can't believe if that's what you'd do"],[2990,3086,"and how you treat me after."],[3086,3199,"I treated you like a princess"],[3199,3294,"for three fucking years."],[3365,3428,"So tell me,"],[3490,3620,"who's the father of the pup?"],[3699,3787,"Caspian."]],"45":[[4,129,"Caspian, it's you."],[212,337,"The pup is yours."],[354,425,"You have to believe me,"],[425,496,"I'd never lie"],[496,608,"about something like this."],[663,729,"Luna Marina,"],[729,971,"I've only ever been with Caspian."],[996,1192,"If Caspian says the pup is not his,"],[1192,1305,"then I believe him."],[1305,1376,"No."],[1430,1522,"That's impossible."],[1580,1730,"Willow has been saving herself"],[1730,1847,"for her coronation."],[1876,2022,"She would never sleep around!"],[2077,2268,"Caspian, don't you remember,"],[2289,2385,"a month ago?"],[2531,2656,"You came home blackout drunk and"],[2677,2815,"you came into my room and"],[2840,2923,"made love to me."],[2994,3178,"I went to talk with our healer and"],[3211,3286,"I'm pregnant."],[3324,3541,"I wanted to tell you privately"],[3603,3745,"after the Luna coronation."],[3820,3874,"Wow,"],[3941,4133,"Alphas really are ruthless."],[4154,4291,"Getting her pregnant and then"],[4291,4429,"tossing her aside?"],[4446,4525,"Right?"],[4542,4671,"Now everyone knows"],[4671,4763,"that Willow is pregnant."],[4775,4925,"If Alpha Caspian leaves her,"],[4954,5059,"nobody will ever want to"],[5059,5117,"mate with her."],[5171,5317,"Alright Willow, you say I'm the father."],[5397,5467,"Where's your proof?"],[5563,5668,"What else can I show you?"],[5668,5759,"What can I show you?"],[5830,5997,"My sister's worked with the healer."],[6026,6118,"Why don't you let her check?"],[6268,6318,"I..."],[6393,6468,"Feeling guilty, huh?"],[6602,6673,"I'll show you."],[6744,6831,"I have nothing to hide."],[7065,7140,"Is she actually"],[7140,7248,"a skilled enough healer"],[7248,7390,"to tell if I'm pregnant?"]],"46":[[125,200,"Mari, what is it?"],[200,283,"Is she lying?"],[542,604,"No."],[763,825,"God."],[917,1051,"The pup is one month along."],[1096,1234,"Willow, this is bullshit"],[1251,1322,"and you know it."],[1322,1459,"Even if I was blackout drunk,"],[1459,1555,"there's no way that you'd be"],[1555,1685,"pregnant with me after one night,"],[1685,1743,"come on."],[1801,1956,"Alpha Caspian, if I may."],[1972,2122,"You've got all of the proof"],[2122,2198,"that you need."],[2198,2385,"You can't live in denial."],[2419,2477,"Caspian,"],[2477,2585,"if she's really pregnant,"],[2585,2681,"we should let this go."],[2723,2957,"No, they almost killed you."],[2977,3161,"They murdered your pup."],[3165,3345,"I'm not gonna let this go!"],[3365,3411,"Caspian,"],[3411,3570,"I know you hate me right now but,"],[3632,3745,"but the pup is yours."],[3807,3899,"I don't want the pup to grow up"],[3899,3974,"without a father."],[4133,4300,"Luna Marina, please."],[4358,4542,"I'm sorry about your pup, but"],[4633,4758,"but the pup is your brother's."],[4821,5075,"And what's mine is yours, even my pup."],[5138,5288,"And please tell Caspian"],[5288,5334,"to forgive me."],[5334,5447,"Tell him to take me back."],[5480,5634,"Tell him to take me back, please."],[5659,5697,"Please."],[5697,5776,"Get your hands - Please."],[5776,5834,"off of her."],[5964,6143,"I'm gonna prove that pup isn't mine."],[6322,6377,"What?"]],"47":[[54,108,"Cas,"],[175,296,"if she's really pregnant,"],[296,454,"casting a bloodline spell"],[479,604,"on a four-week old fetus"],[604,734,"could cause a miscarriage."],[746,796,"Mari."],[796,913,"It's not worth it."],[913,1009,"Let it go. - Mari."],[1009,1263,"Mari, they almost killed you."],[1334,1447,"You're my sister."],[1514,1584,"They killed your pup."],[1584,1739,"I'll never get to meet my nephew."],[1776,1972,"I'm not gonna let this go."],[2127,2189,"Never."],[2252,2369,"He's ruthless."],[2410,2598,"If the spell shows it's his pup"],[2606,2756,"and Willow has a miscarriage,"],[2761,2882,"he'll never forgive himself."],[2886,2977,"Of course he will."],[3023,3174,"He's putting two lives at risk"],[3174,3315,"just to prove his Luna wrong."],[3349,3399,"Shut up."],[3432,3536,"Alpha Caspian,"],[3553,3728,"my daughter is not only pregnant"],[3728,3887,"with the Bloodveil pack heir,"],[3916,4183,"but that is my grandchild too."],[4225,4408,"If something happens to them,"],[4483,4688,"will you take full responsibility?"],[4733,4838,"Luna Marina"],[4888,5117,"already proved that Willow is pregnant."],[5184,5397,"Caspian should claim her"],[5417,5634,"and we cast the bloodline spell"],[5663,5789,"after the pup comes!"],[5805,5922,"Yes, please."],[5985,6147,"Please, let's not be too hasty."],[6160,6231,"No!"]],"48":[[0,66,"No!"],[283,467,"I am getting justice for my sister."],[500,558,"Now."],[608,671,"Caspian."],[784,950,"How could you do this to our pup?"],[1130,1280,"I won't agree to a bloodline spell."],[1280,1338,"I won't."],[1372,1501,"Luna Marina, you know"],[1501,1597,"that a mother would do anything"],[1597,1689,"to protect her pup."],[1735,1893,"Please tell Caspian not to hurt it."],[1926,2089,"If Caspian wants to do this,"],[2147,2235,"I won't stop him."],[2285,2377,"How could you?"],[2477,2631,"Heartless, right?"],[2736,2852,"I'm sorry Willow, but"],[2948,3069,"my heartlessness"],[3128,3290,"doesn't hold a candle to yours."],[3528,3582,"Fine!"],[3774,3903,"If you're not gonna stop,"],[3903,4079,"then I'm gonna end my life and my pup,"],[4079,4208,"right here and right now."]],"49":[[20,133,"Guard, stop her!"],[154,350,"No, Caspian, this is your pup too!"],[396,492,"If you're not going to-"],[492,571,"Get off!"],[667,850,"If you're not going to take care of it then,"],[950,1038,"then you don't deserve to be"],[1038,1155,"the pup's father."],[1176,1255,"Fine."],[1334,1438,"If it proves the pup is mine,"],[1438,1543,"I'll compensate you for it."],[1568,1651,"Oh."],[1668,1735,"Alpha Caspian,"],[1735,1860,"why didn't you say so sooner?"],[1860,1922,"That's wonderful."],[1993,2135,"Willow, please say yes."],[2164,2214,"No."],[2293,2435,"If the spell comes out true,"],[2435,2673,"then will you still crown me"],[2673,2773,"as your Luna?"],[2994,3053,"Hell no."],[3136,3286,"After everything you've just done?"],[3365,3482,"No, the pup will be my heir"],[3482,3574,"and you'll get nothing."],[3582,3657,"Caspian,"],[3691,3791,"my daughter has been nothing"],[3791,3941,"but a loyal mate to you."],[3974,4116,"How can you be so heartless?"],[4133,4241,"Alpha Caspian,"],[4241,4391,"if the pup is yours,"],[4391,4525,"you should take care of"],[4525,4692,"the mother and the pup."],[4746,4938,"What kind of Alpha protects the pup"],[4938,5088,"and tosses aside the mom?"],[5130,5321,"My choices are not up for discussion."],[5334,5455,"You'll obey what I say."],[5555,5676,"Now, get me a witch."]],"50":[[16,133,"Getting cold feet there, Willow?"],[212,246,"No."],[291,417,"No, I'm a hundred percent sure"],[417,492,"the pup is yours."],[538,642,"I've only ever been with you."],[704,742,"Okay."],[867,938,"We'll see what you say"],[938,1034,"after the spell is cast."]],"51":[[329,500,"In a few short minutes,"],[554,838,"the spell will conjure the truth."],[1443,1534,"And then, Willow,"],[1693,1793,"we'll know the real truth."],[1864,1939,"And you're gonna regret"],[1939,2052,"everything you said to me."],[2469,2565,"Alpha Caspian,"],[2565,2694,"we've got the security footage"],[2694,2794,"from your mansion."],[2973,3011,"No!"],[3061,3144,"Let go!"],[3215,3249,"No!"],[3249,3357,"Let go of me."],[3395,3586,"I want my mate back, you mangy whore!"],[3841,3912,"I see."],[3933,4029,"So Willow led the pack,"],[4029,4124,"but the rest of you had"],[4124,4366,"no problem assaulting my sister."],[4366,4562,"The three of you step forward, now."]],"52":[[792,971,"Sir, I'm sorry."],[1009,1071,"You're sorry?"],[1184,1259,"You think that's enough?"],[1305,1422,"But, but..."],[1463,1589,"Okay, get them out of my sight."],[1689,1797,"The council can deal with you."],[1797,1960,"Lock them away in the dungeons to rot."],[1968,2047,"Yes, my Alpha."],[2056,2152,"What, What?"],[2168,2268,"No, no, no, no, no."],[2277,2423,"I, I can't sleep with the rats."],[2481,2623,"Please, Alpha Caspian,"],[2644,2865,"please forgive us?"],[2886,2977,"Please!"],[3003,3215,"We were just acting on Willow's orders."],[3228,3328,"We're all too powerless"],[3328,3436,"to stand up to her."],[3461,3624,"It, it was all Willow's idea."],[3624,3762,"She threatened to rip our throats out"],[3762,3874,"if we didn't listen to her."],[3874,3962,"Bullshit!"],[4020,4108,"I never threatened you!"],[4108,4250,"You all acted on your own accord."],[4287,4341,"Liar!"],[4379,4550,"If you haven't been marked by the Alpha"],[4550,4612,"of the Bloodville pack,"],[4612,4750,"do you really think we'd listen to you?"],[4796,4942,"Who cares about your stupid family?"],[4950,5059,"That's enough!"],[5075,5180,"Get them out of my sight."],[5246,5363,"No, no, no, no, no, no."],[5384,5426,"What?"],[5430,5501,"No, please!"],[5501,5559,"Please!"],[5559,5689,"Alpha, please!"],[5872,5955,"Alpha,"],[6039,6164,"I have more security footage."],[6197,6256,"It's all there."],[6302,6352,"No."],[6418,6481,"You can't!"],[6481,6531,"No!"],[6552,6589,"Hey!"],[6610,6690,"Get off of her."],[6835,6894,"Okay."]],"53":[[1105,1151,"You."],[1543,1664,"You used your twisted tongue"],[1664,1947,"to insult my sister five times."],[2014,2173,"You're gonna get on your fucking knees."],[2293,2435,"And you're gonna drink the wolfsbane."],[2485,2585,"And then I'll let you go."],[2681,2756,"Yes sir."],[2869,2944,"Thank you, sir."],[4066,4112,"You."],[4175,4291,"You humiliated"],[4366,4466,"and insulted my sister,"],[4475,4629,"and encouraged everyone else"],[4646,4704,"to attack her."],[4704,4750,"And you don't know"],[4750,4859,"when to shut the fuck up."],[4888,4996,"No, no no, no."],[5046,5117,"Alpha."],[5146,5226,"Your family"],[5280,5430,"and all your heirs are banished"],[5430,5580,"from our kingdom forever."],[5643,5709,"And you."],[5709,5797,"Yes, you."],[5826,5960,"You're gonna get on your fucking knees."],[5960,6026,"And you're gonna finish"],[6026,6106,"that wolfsbane."],[6193,6260,"Then you're gonna get the"],[6260,6356,"fuck out of here."]],"54":[[291,383,"Alpha Caspian,"],[492,600,"I, I already told you,"],[692,850,"I, I had nothing to do with this."],[913,1051,"It was all my mom and my sister."],[1055,1222,"You worthless, ungrateful mutt!"],[1251,1409,"How can you do this to your own mother?"],[1430,1689,"I am the only son of the Hale family."],[1705,1776,"I'm doing this"],[1776,1910,"to preserve our bloodline!"],[2006,2102,"Why can't you just"],[2102,2214,"sacrifice yourself for me?"],[2214,2327,"After everything you've done,"],[2327,2402,"you expect me"],[2402,2573,"just to let you go scott-free?"],[2652,2702,"Really?"],[2790,2986,"No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no."],[2986,3119,"Alpha Caspian, please."],[3119,3224,"I'm so sorry."],[3244,3299,"I know."],[3303,3365,"I, I know."],[3365,3474,"I know I was wrong!"],[3474,3720,"I'll do, I'll do whatever you say!"],[3720,3832,"I'll be your guard dog,"],[3832,3953,"I'll do whatever you want!"],[3953,4058,"Whenever you want!"],[4074,4129,"I don't want you"],[4129,4216,"following me anywhere."],[4216,4337,"You disgust me."],[4571,4642,"Then I'll disappear."],[4671,4742,"I'll, I'll..."],[4763,4971,"uh, you'll never see me again."],[5005,5096,"I mean, come on."],[5125,5263,"I'm just a low-ranking wolf."],[5263,5426,"I mean, what's killing me"],[5426,5530,"gonna even accomplish?"],[5530,5680,"Because I have principles!"],[5822,6076,"You don't lay a finger on my sister"],[6131,6281,"or cause her harm, or"],[6322,6435,"you killed her pup."],[6531,6694,"You expect me just to let you go"],[6706,6810,"for free?"],[6810,6986,"Please, Alpha."],[7148,7378,"What can I do to earn my freedom?"],[7565,7640,"I have an idea."],[7724,7849,"Whatever limb you used"],[7941,8066,"to attack my sister,"],[8124,8266,"cut that off with a silver dagger."],[8337,8408,"I'll let you go."],[8629,8671,"What?"]],"55":[[29,225,"But, Alpha, if,"],[304,513,"if I cut myself with a silver dagger,"],[513,713,"then the wound will never heal."],[829,1101,"No, uh, I'm so, I'm so sorry!"],[1101,1192,"I swear!"],[1209,1380,"I didn't know that she was your sister!"],[1380,1555,"I thought that she was just some,"],[1593,1805,"just some bond-breaking bitch!"],[1822,2031,"So if she was just some ordinary wolf,"],[2064,2147,"my sister,"],[2206,2481,"it'd be okay to kill her and her pup?"],[2481,2544,"No, no, no."],[2544,2619,"That is not what I meant."],[2619,2694,"Is that what you mean?"],[2694,2752,"No, no, no!"],[2752,2806,"That is not what I-"],[2806,2902,"Look at me!"],[3078,3148,"You have one minute."],[3224,3294,"Do it,"],[3349,3474,"or I'll have someone do it for you."],[3524,3670,"I, I, I..."],[3682,3795,"Alpha Caspian, please."],[3837,3974,"Rowen's just a baby!"],[3974,4016,"He..."],[4016,4124,"you, please let him go."],[4124,4229,"He didn't know any better."],[4229,4325,"Alpha, please!"],[4346,4421,"Don't do this."],[4512,4688,"If Rowen is hurt permanently,"],[4688,4808,"who's gonna take care of us"],[4808,4917,"when we're old?"],[4950,4996,"Ten."],[5005,5071,"No!"],[5071,5117,"Oh, no."],[5117,5246,"Please, please, don't!"],[5280,5330,"Five."],[5330,5518,"Caspian, please, wait!"],[5526,5568,"Guards."],[5568,5647,"Wait!"],[5672,5718,"No."],[5751,5830,"No, no!"],[5839,5922,"No, no!"],[5922,6060,"No, no, no, wait, wait!"],[6060,6197,"I know Willow's secret!"],[6498,6644,"And you need to know it!"]],"56":[[8,62,"Wait."],[412,517,"You know Willow's secret?"],[596,633,"Yeah."],[725,792,"She's been keeping"],[792,880,"something from you."],[921,1059,"Only the two of us know about it."],[1063,1159,"Rowen, shut up!"],[1197,1284,"I'll rip your tongue out!"],[1284,1359,"No, I just-"],[1372,1455,"He's, he's not..."],[1455,1576,"I, I haven't lied to you"],[1576,1651,"about anything."],[1680,1851,"I swear, Alpha,"],[1851,2047,"in the Moon Goddess's name,"],[2056,2214,"that I am telling the truth!"],[2252,2373,"And I'll tell you"],[2423,2523,"if you just promise,"],[2523,2644,"please, just let me go."],[2694,2744,"Tell me."],[2794,3044,"You are a generous man, Alpha."],[3086,3182,"I know, I know that"],[3182,3278,"you will show me mercy"],[3278,3386,"once you know the truth."],[3420,3503,"No, Caspian."],[3503,3653,"I'm not, I'm not lying to you"],[3653,3707,"about anything!"],[3707,3812,"You can't listen to him!"],[3837,3966,"Then why do you look so scared?"],[3983,4083,"I'm not, it's just,"],[4133,4229,"Rowen would say anything"],[4229,4320,"to save himself right now!"],[4320,4500,"You can't believe his lies!"],[4521,4633,"I wouldn't be so sure."],[4775,4821,"Rowen,"],[4913,5055,"this is your last chance."],[5576,5680,"I know"],[5830,6160,"who the real father of Willow's pup is."]],"57":[[175,279,"And I'll tell you,"],[358,571,"if you just promise"],[654,746,"to let me go."],[809,892,"The pup's father?"],[892,1063,"Is that even really a secret?"],[1188,1259,"The bloodline spell"],[1259,1430,"hasn't revealed its truth yet."],[1484,1672,"If the pup really isn't Alpha Caspian's,"],[1672,1785,"Willow's in deep shit."],[1830,2052,"Rowen, what are you doing?"],[2118,2285,"You can't destroy your sister's"],[2285,2410,"reputation with lies."],[2410,2548,"I'm not lying."],[2623,2886,"Willow's pup isn't Caspian's."],[2915,3065,"And I know because..."],[3474,3591,"I'm the father."],[3641,3707,"What?"]],"58":[[8,75,"What?"],[133,237,"What's going on?"],[308,433,"That's his sister."],[467,608,"If Rowen's telling the truth,"],[617,717,"that's disgusting."],[729,800,"Rowen,"],[884,1038,"you understand what you're saying."],[1071,1263,"Yes, I do."],[1297,1405,"And I have proof."],[1518,1668,"And I will let you listen to it."],[1730,1897,"Only if you promise that"],[1897,1985,"you will let us go."],[2039,2114,"Swear it."],[2156,2223,"I swear on the"],[2223,2327,"Goddesses of the moon,"],[2435,2502,"I'll let you go."],[3240,3395,"I tried to get Caspian to sleep with me,"],[3395,3499,"but he refused."],[3528,3636,"I need to get pregnant."],[3695,3799,"I need you to help me."],[3816,3887,"Are you kidding?"],[3887,3928,"We're..."],[3962,4108,"We're not actually blood related."],[4179,4341,"You're a bastard pup dad snuck home."],[4408,4546,"Mom had me before she met dad,"],[4546,4625,"what's the big deal?"],[4846,5075,"You piece of shit!"],[5159,5326,"You took our son and replaced him"],[5326,5463,"with your own bastard!"],[5622,5868,"Mom, none of this matters right now!"],[5926,6085,"All that matters is that"],[6085,6285,"Caspian shows us mercy."],[6360,6456,"Alpha Caspian,"],[6535,6677,"I told you Willow's secret"],[6744,6873,"and I told you mine."],[6986,7023,"Now,"],[7094,7257,"please, will you keep your word"],[7340,7482,"and just let us go?"],[7549,7595,"Fine."],[7736,7878,"But first, there's something I must do."]],"59":[[1038,1080,"Willow,"],[1710,1768,"I,"],[1818,1960,"Alpha Caspian Brooks,"],[2006,2189,"officially reject you,"],[2239,2323,"Willow Hale,"],[2331,2431,"as my mate."],[2848,2919,"Now,"],[3069,3119,"Alpha,"],[3207,3269,"can we go?"],[3294,3361,"Oh."],[3528,3586,"Not yet."],[3649,3745,"The guards will let you out"],[3745,3820,"at nightfall."],[3866,3974,"And there's a, uh,"],[4074,4291,"lovely surprise waiting for you."],[4350,4446,"A surprise?"],[4950,5042,"Are those?"],[5109,5184,"Rogue wolves."],[5276,5351,"I gave them permission"],[5351,5451,"to hunt until dawn."],[5551,5622,"They'll be waiting for you."],[5630,5801,"Oh, and, they're hungry."],[6377,6427,"Mari,"],[6564,6639,"let's go home."]]}